*&quot;Anatomy of Restlessness: Selected Writings 1969-1989&quot; (1995, reprinted 1996); reprinted as &quot;Anatomy of Restlessness: Uncollected Writings&quot; (1997)
*&quot;Winding Paths&quot; (1998)
*&quot;Under the Sun: The Letters of Bruce Chatwin&quot; (2012)

